GDAL package for @TARGET_TRIPLE@

Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@

Components:
- GEOS @GEOS_VERSION@
- libyaml @LIBYAML_VERSION@
- PROJ @PROJ_VERSION@
- libgeotiff @LIBGEOTIFF_VERSION@
- minizip from zlib 1.3.2
- FreeXL @FREEXL_VERSION@
- libspatialite @LIBSPATIALITE_VERSION@
- GDAL @GDAL_VERSION@

This prefix is layered on top of postgresql_dependencies and image for the same
target. PostgreSQL/libpq support is intentionally not enabled in this package;
PostGIS combines this SDK with the PostgreSQL package separately.
